task.summary: UX additions - Download button disabled if there is nothing to be downloaded Search Button is defaulted, so hitting enter will execute search
Cleaned up the code a little, fixed some redundancies
Removed Third Party RSS Parser, made a custom one. Added new data fields - Size, Seeds and Peers
Added new data fields to display in the UI - Size, Seeds and Peers
Forgot to changes values meant for testing purposes. Fixed now.

Added size in the ComboBox selector list
Added Min and Max size to prevent the user from changing the size of the window.
Improved UI, torrent details now show up in a rectangle below the ComboBox. Changed app icon.

Added a HTML parser to get Magnet links from backup RSS feeds (Torrentz.eu).
Even though it is better to keep one consistent feed and have lesser code, I am not removing the primary RSS feed as parsing HTML is slower.
Refactored code, reduced global variable usage. Added a "Open" button to open the torrent web page.

Now shows size of the torrent in the ComboBox selector when using the backup feed.
Some refactoring and removing redundant code as well.
